derivation: from G1 (ἀνεξιχνίαστος) (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of a compound of G1537 (ἀνεξιχνίαστος) and a derivative of G2487 (ἀνεξιχνίαστος);
strongs_def: not tracked out, i.e. (by implication) untraceable
outline: 1. that cannot be searched out, that cannot be comprehended
